      </div>
      <div class="avail-notice" role="note" aria-label="Tour availability">
        <svg width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink:0; margin-top:0.1rem;"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg>
        <span><strong>Departure windows:</strong> Weekday departures are available from 5:00 PM – 7:00 PM. Weekend departures are available from 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM. All Point Barrow tours are weather- and condition-dependent. Bookings are requests and confirmed by Robin after review.</span>
      </div>
